quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  16,35,"∆Āen sirku…ďe wi'i: \"Sinno Alla muuyuno, men rewataano gaanin Makko hay huunde, wanaa menen wanaa baabiraa…ďe amen; men harmintaa- no gaanin Makko hay huunde\". Ko wano non adi- noo…ďe …ďen gerdunoo. Taw si no fawiiii Nulaa…ďe …ďen si wanaa yottingol …ďanngina"
  16,36,"Gom…óii Men imminii e kala mofte Nulaa…óo, wonnde rewee Alla, wo…ó…óito…óon bewnay…ói …óin. Hino e ma…ď…ďe on Mo Alla fewni, hino e ma…ď…ďe kadi on mo majjere nden jojji e mun. Yiilee ka leydi, ndaaron ko honno battane fennoo…ďe …ďen wa'unoo"
  16,37,"Si a rer…óii e peewal ma…ď…ďe, [anndu] pellet, Alla fewnataa on Mo o majjini, alanaa …ďe kadi walloo…ďe"
  16,38,"∆Āe woondirii Alla ha…ótirde goondooje ma…ď…ďe: \"Alla immintintaa on maayu…óo\". Wanaa non! ∆äum ko fodoore goonga ka Makko, ko woni tun, ko …ďuri …óuu…óude e yim…ďe …ďe anndaa"
  16,39,"(O immintiniroyay …ďe) fii yo O …ďannginan …ďe ko …ďe luutondiraynoo e mun, e fii yo …ďen yeddu…ďe anndu wonnde hari ko …ďe fenoo…ďe"
  16,40,"Anndee daalol Amen wonannde huunde, si Men faandike nde, Men wi'anay nde tun: \"Laato\", nde laatoo"